 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/revolutionary-imaging-technique-unlocks-secrets-of-matter-at-extreme-speeds</guid></item><item><title>量子突破：使用量子点将不可破解的密钥发送超过 120 公里</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-breakthrough-unhackable-keys-sent-over-120-km-using-quantum-dots</link><description>基于量子点的时间仓QKD实现稳定、远距离的安全通信，具有实用性能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-breakthrough-unhackable-keys-sent-over-120-km-using-quantum-dots.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 11:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-breakthrough-unhackable-keys-sent-over-120-km-using-quantum-dots</guid></item><item><title>纳米医学如何进入您的细胞并从内到外治疗您</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-nanomedicine-gets-inside-your-cells-and-treats-you-from-the-inside-out</link><description>加拿大人每天吞服数百万粒药片来治疗&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-nanomedicine-gets-inside-your-cells-and-treats-you-from-the-inside-out.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 11:36:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-nanomedicine-gets-inside-your-cells-and-treats-you-from-the-inside-out</guid></item><item><title>纳米抗体修复细胞内错误折叠的 CFTR，增强囊性纤维化的功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nanobody-repairs-misfolded-cftr-inside-cells-boosting-function-in-cystic-fibrosis</link><description>微小的抗体成分可以从根本上改变囊性纤维化的治疗方法：研究人员首次成功开发出一种所谓的纳米抗体，它可以直接渗透到人体细胞中，并可以修复囊性纤维化最常受影响的氯离子通道。这种创新的治疗方法是柏林夏里特医学大学和莱布尼茨分子药理学研究所 (FMP) 的团队合作开发的。现在结果已经&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nanobody-repairs-misfolded-cftr-inside-cells-boosting-function-in-cystic-fibrosis.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 11:21:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nanobody-repairs-misfolded-cftr-inside-cells-boosting-function-in-cystic-fibrosis</guid></item><item><title>研究表明，食用超加工食品的人肌肉健康状况较差</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/people-who-consume-ultra-processed-foods-have-worse-muscle-health-study-suggests</link><description>研究人员发现，无论有膝骨关节炎风险的人群的卡路里或脂肪摄入量、体力活动或社会人口因素如何，富含超加工食品的饮食与大腿肌肉内储存的脂肪量较高有关。研究结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/people-who-consume-ultra-processed-foods-have-worse-muscle-health-study-suggests.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 11:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/people-who-consume-ultra-processed-foods-have-worse-muscle-health-study-suggests</guid></item><item><title>童年严重疟疾后的长期认知能力和学业成绩</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/long-term-cognitive-ability-and-academic-achievement-after-childhood-severe-malaria</link><description>在有脑型疟疾病史或严重疟疾贫血的儿童中，长期随访显示，在疟疾发作后 4 至 15 年进行评估时，与未受影响的儿童相比，其整体认知能力和数学成绩较低。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/long-term-cognitive-ability-and-academic-achievement-after-childhood-severe-malaria.png" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 10:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/long-term-cognitive-ability-and-academic-achievement-after-childhood-severe-malaria</guid></item><item><title>IGF-1 信号传导减少的长寿效应取决于线粒体基因组的稳定性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-longevity-effects-of-reduced-igf-1-signaling-depend-on-the-stability-of-the-mitochondrial-genome</link><description>这一见解对于抗衰老疗法的发展具有重大意义。首先，他们认为线粒体DNA完整性不仅仅是衰老的众多标志之一，而且是其他标志的基础。当该平台被破坏时，蛋白质稳态或 DNA 修复等下游标志就无法通过典型手段发挥作用。其次，它表明，当应用于线粒体损伤程度较高的生物体或组织时，针对营养感应途径的干预措施可能会失败，甚至适得其反。因此，下一代老年保护治疗必须在不同的衰老模型中进行测试，包括那些结合了多种特征的模型，以更好地了解其功效的范围和界限。最后，通过提高线粒体基因组稳定性的措施可以放大这些治疗的功效。虽然 IGF-1 信号传导的减少并没有改变 WT 或&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-longevity-effects-of-reduced-igf-1-signaling-depend-on-the-stability-of-the-mitochondrial-genome2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 10:36:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-longevity-effects-of-reduced-igf-1-signaling-depend-on-the-stability-of-the-mitochondrial-genome</guid></item><item><title>零股</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/odd-lots</link><description>投资播客 · 彭博社的 Joe Weisenthal 和 Tracy Alloway 探讨金融、市场和经济领域最有趣的话题。每周一和周四加入对话。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/odd-lots.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 10:21:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/odd-lots</guid></item></channel></rss>